features: 4 styles: Argomax 100 piece cleaning swab set has 4 shapes of precision tips for removing impurities from surfaces in tiny, hard-to-reach areas, with different shapes for your different applications and needs, allowing you to choose the flexibility.

Wide range of uses: foam cleaning swabs can be used as a gun cleaning swab, camera sensor cleaning swab, optical lens cleaning swab, printer cleaning swab, circuit board cleaning swab, computer, electronic cleaning swab, jewellery cleaning swab, craft cleaning swab, kitchen hood or car ventilation, etc.

Flexible and durable: the cleaning sticks are lightweight and flexible and allow access to very small areas and crevices, making them particularly suitable for removing grease and other impurities in small areas.
